{"tid":2309401,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許智峯訪丹麥 促歐洲國家為香港抗爭者提供避難所","createTime":"2020-12-02T13:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T14:35:33.000Z","uid":39464,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7db20a1457d101161a10bcd78bf7b35bbfd7aa63","tid":2309401,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:42:03.000Z","msg":"民主黨前立法會議員許智峯應邀到丹麥訪問，促請歐洲國家跟隨英國做法，向香港抗爭者提供避難所。許智峯透過電郵回應美聯社查詢，他形容，香港狀況日益惡劣，令全球明白香港不再是一個自由城市，十分重要；邀請他訪問的丹麥組織指，許智峯此行是希望改變丹麥政府的立場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2369035\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2369035&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOUwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=e5756eda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2369035</a>"},{"pid":"1a0ddca5ef8854cac284c453bd9451b0fa67fa86","tid":2309401,"uid":66178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:43:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2942313eeb9d100d7042a12500b476c35063a930","tid":2309401,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05f4b95af73e43678e84d81e1d4dcde5e9f9b99","tid":2309401,"uid":210558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83cd7e9532a01aab01a017c21a78fc7104610b7","tid":2309401,"uid":339384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c55dcc3c8bd8ac38ac28bc0979743d9acce89e","tid":2309401,"uid"